    <section id="about-me" class="section alt">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>15 years old FPV pilot.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="two-column">
            <p>I started flying drones since I was 9 years old. At first they were these cheap china drones with the 720p camera .</p>
            <p>Now I'm flying with serious equipment and some skill. I love flying in nice landscape scenarios, they are just beautiful.</p>
            <p>I also work for clients, if you are interested then DM me per Instagram. I will respond as soon as possible</p>
        </div>
