            <li><h3>2024 - Bought my first ever quality drone</h3><p>DJI Mini 3 in December 2024</p></li>
            <li><h3>2025 - Gathering informations about FPV</h3><p>Research about FPV and DJI FPV bought.</p></li>
            <li><h3>March 2026</h3><p>Built the 5". First clips with my 5".</p></li>
